Class HeartyMeal

  • java.lang.Object
    • HealingItem
      • HeartyMeal

  • public class HeartyMeal
extends HealingItem
    Instances of HeartyMeal represent a type of healing item the player can obtain in the game. Each object represents one healing item. A new object should be created when the team obtains a Hearty Meal item, and deleted when it has been incremented the maximum number of times.
